high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the countertop.
Turn right and pick the spatula from the countertop.
Put the spatula inside the sink and rinse it off.
Pick it back and place the spatula near the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the spatula near the sink.

high_descs: Turn left go straight walk to the countertop
Take the ladle near to the oven
Turn around then right to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink, pour the water and take it back.
Place the ladle near to the sink
anns.task_desc: Take the ladle near to the oven, clean it and place it near to the sink.

high_descs: Turn left to reach the kitchen countertop next to the microwave.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Turn left to reach the sink.
Wash the ladle in the sink and take it out.
Put the ladle on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed ladle on the counter.
